RP MedicareComplete program through UnitedHealthcare. Coverage is available for members with pre-existing conditions and does not require physical exams.\u000a\u000a6. Credit cards \u2014 The AARP credit card from Chase is designed for members, who are eligible for a $200 bonus cash back after spending $500 on purchases in the first three months. There are also cash back rewards at restaurants, gas stations, and other services.\u000a\u000aImportant: Gingrich and Reagan Video Goes Viral. See It Now
