aVSteve Bannon will be able to better serve President Donald Trump now that he's out as White House chief strategist and back as executive chairman of conservative news website Breitbart, David Horowitz, author of the New York Times bestseller "Big Agenda," told Newsmax TV on Monday.\u000a\u000a"By moving outside, he's going to be able to target all those enemies of Trump within the White House and to rally the only real weapon that Trump has\u2026 the real base on which he stands, and that is the people," Horowitz said to Miranda Khan on Newsmax's "America Talks Live."\u000a\u000a"Trump was elected by an electorate that wasn't fooled by the lying fake news media, that wasn't fooled by all these phony cries of racism. Those people are what Trump's survival depends on.\u000a\u000a"And with his ally, Steve Bannon, outside but in probably the most significant media organization, certainly internet organization out there, this is very good for Trump."\u000a\u000aImportant: Newsmax TV is available on DirecTV Ch. 349, U-Verse 1220, and FiOS 615. If your cable operator does not have Newsmax TV just call and ask them to put us on \u2013 Call toll-free 1-844-500-6397 and we will connect you right away to your cable operator!\u000a\u000aFor more places to Find Newsmax TV \u2013 Click Here Now\u000a\u000aHorowitz, liberal-turned-conservative and founder of The David Horowitz Freedom Center, added that Bannon's departure takes "some of the heat off" Trump because of charges by liberals that Bannon has deep alt-right ties.\u000a\u000a"Trump is in a bind when somebody has been targeted. I mean a disgraceful campaign against Steve Bannon. The true racists in our society are all those Democrats and liberals who attack Steve Bannon, calling him an anti-Semite, a white nationalist, a neo-Nazi," Horowitz said.\u000a\u000a"Bannon can get him tremendous support on the outside \u2026 How did Trump get in office in the first place? He got it by mobilizing people and Bannon is very well situated to do that now."\u000a\u000a"Big Agenda: President Trump's Plan to Save America" is published by Humanix Books.
